---
title: Fish ID
order: 3
blurb: My signature species identification series, helping you recognise the marine life you see.
---

Fish ID is my signature series, a growing, searchable library that helps divers
and ocean lovers put names to the species they encounter. Each reel pairs real
footage with the key features to look for, so the next time you see it, you'll
know exactly what it is.

It's the series that turns a nice dive into a learning one, and it grows with
every dive I do.
